FeedPackage.Description: dotMongo is a C#.NET open source project that (tries to) extend and simplify MongoDB database function calls for .NET developers. The project wraps around the MongoDB .NET Driver (v2.2.3) and handles; - Creating MongoDB client and connecting to the database by parsing an XML configuration Connection String. - Serialization of BsonDocument to Generic C# object. - Converting basic Lambda Expressions to Filter Definition.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: v0.0.1 (Build: Jan-6-2016) - Initial Release - New : Basic query functions e.g. Where, Single, First. - New : Basic CRUD e.g. Insert, Delete. - New : Lambda expression to Filter definition. - New : Ping method. - New : Connection string parser. - New : Credential authentication when creating MongoDB client. - Upd : Upgraded MongoDB .NET driver dependency to version 2.2.3.
FeedPackage.Summary: Extend and simplify MongoDB .NET driver
FeedPackage.Title: dotMongo
